Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.46,0:00:01.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zanpakuto…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.36,0:00:07.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Their shape and abilities are\Nbased on their Soul Reaper's soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.60,0:00:10.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Soul Reapers gain power
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.86,0:00:15.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,by learning their names\Nand synergizing with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.93,0:00:21.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They are born with Soul Reapers\Nand die with Soul Reapers.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.80,0:00:24.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is what Zanpakuto are.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.63,0:02:10.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.20,0:02:27.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you know him very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.16,0:02:30.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Head Captain\NGenryusai Yamamoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.90,0:02:34.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.13,0:02:40.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those three are Zanpakuto.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.96,0:02:42.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Their powers rival each other
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.73,0:02:47.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so they've been frozen in\Nthat state for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.53,0:02:50.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Their powers rival each other…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.93,0:03:21.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.13,0:03:25.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make him change\Nhis Spiritual Pressure!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.44,0:03:27.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't blame us if\Nyou get blown away
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.01,0:03:29.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,by his fluctuating\NSpiritual Pressure!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.23,0:03:30.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.34,0:03:38.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They don't really listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.20,0:03:43.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's quite troublesome\Nfor the Head Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.20,0:04:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Byakuya! You…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.20,0:04:39.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Damn it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.78,0:04:43.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.33,0:04:50.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wait…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.20,0:04:57.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Old Man Yama's whereabouts?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.70,0:04:59.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that true?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.40,0:05:04.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's just\Nthe most likely place
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.31,0:05:07.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the Head Captain would be.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.23,0:05:11.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I found the Head Captain's\NSpiritual Pressure there again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.10,0:05:18.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.46,0:05:20.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's not much point in\Nwaiting for them to come to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.13,0:05:23.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not in our nature to wait,\Nafter all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.50,0:05:26.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Ken! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.04,0:05:29.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go looking for Old Man!\NCome on!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.42,0:05:32.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think you're confusing this\Nwith a game of hide-and-seek.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.16,0:05:33.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.70,0:05:38.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The guy I have to slash\Nis probably there, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.20,0:05:40.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.33,0:05:44.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But try not to slash\Nthe General Captain by mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.96,0:05:49.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That Old Man wouldn't quite rest in\Npeace if he's slashed by accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.56,0:05:53.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about it?\NWill you two be coming with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.46,0:06:13.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.69,0:06:16.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your idea of an interesting day\Nis so exciting
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.34,0:06:20.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that other people's hearts\Nwould stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.12,0:06:21.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a cruel thing to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.99,0:06:23.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.53,0:06:26.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I was released\Nfrom my master,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.71,0:06:30.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that it was the beginning\Nof a more interesting life.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.30,0:06:34.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were easily defeated\Nby your master too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.30,0:06:38.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! That was your fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.15,0:06:39.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.29,0:06:42.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The same thing happened to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.63,0:06:45.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?\NYou seem rather calm today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.26,0:06:50.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I do agree\Nthat this is boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.73,0:07:01.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.80,0:07:21.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kazeshini?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.12,0:07:23.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez. Don't scare us like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.80,0:07:27.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kazeshini!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.13,0:07:31.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.86,0:07:37.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no…\NThese wounds are bad…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.47,0:07:41.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I'm surprised he was\Nable to come back here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.00,0:07:43.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.26,0:08:05.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad you could\Nmake it back, Kazeshini.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.30,0:08:09.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rest up and heal your wounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.66,0:08:14.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Muramasa…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.90,0:08:16.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Kazeshini?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.83,0:08:19.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me ask you one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.32,0:08:20.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.86,0:08:24.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You told me to follow\Nmy true instincts, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.13,0:08:26.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.38,0:08:32.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My true instinct is to reap\Nthe lives of Soul Reapers!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.36,0:08:34.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.55,0:08:39.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My goal is to release Zanpakuto\Nfrom Soul Reapers.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.80,0:08:44.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why is there\Na Soul Reaper over there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.30,0:08:58.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Byakuya Kuchiki\Nplays a crucial role
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.10,0:09:00.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in achieving our greater goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.53,0:09:04.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With your help, Byakuya was\Nable to make it back safely.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.23,0:09:07.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am very thankful.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.16,0:09:11.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But why do we have to get\Nhurt for a Soul Reaper?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.16,0:09:17.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though we have\Na greater goal,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.96,0:09:20.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it saddens me that people\Nhave to get hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.40,0:09:25.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there's no need to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.66,0:09:31.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as we have\NGenryusai Yamamoto,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.60,0:09:34.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they cannot do anything to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.46,0:09:38.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're close to achieving our goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.36,0:09:48.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They should be getting desperate.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.90,0:09:52.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but please hold out\Nfor just a little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.93,0:10:06.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This certainly is Genryusai's\NSpiritual Pressure…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.80,0:10:10.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I also sense some\Npowerful barrier.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.86,0:10:14.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Muramasa must have been\Nunable to control Ryujinjakka
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.63,0:10:18.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and sealed Old Man Yama\Nwithin a barrier.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.30,0:10:21.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess we're fortunate that we
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.25,0:10:23.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Ndidn't have to take on Ryujinjakka.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.73,0:10:27.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, the Old Man\Nis in here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.99,0:10:30.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. That's for certain.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.76,0:10:35.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But this cave is like a maze.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.56,0:10:39.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.00,0:10:43.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Zanpakuto appear to be\Nusing a different entrance.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.53,0:10:47.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If their hideout is in here,\Nwe must be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.00,0:10:49.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.80,0:10:52.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's quit talking and\Njust charge on in!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.60,0:10:54.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! Go, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.97,0:10:56.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ken! Go, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.91,0:10:58.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do it! Go, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.70,0:11:03.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly… There's no point in\Nmaking plans when he's around.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.35,0:11:06.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, now's not the time to wait\Nand see what they're going to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.00,0:11:08.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We should go too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.40,0:11:18.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo, we're going in from\Na different entrance.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.20,0:11:22.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.83,0:11:44.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Soul Reapers have come.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.73,0:11:45.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.43,0:12:09.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it… This sucks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.60,0:12:16.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I charged in, but it's so dark\NI don't know where I'm going.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.20,0:12:20.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Yachiru! Which way\Ndo you think I should go?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.79,0:12:23.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see… That way!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.43,0:12:25.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't see which way\Nyou're pointing!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.86,0:12:27.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, it's this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.71,0:12:28.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop that, you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.82,0:12:30.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't pull my ears!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.03,0:12:39.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoruichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.32,0:12:40.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.70,0:12:41.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I ask you one thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.80,0:12:43.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.66,0:12:46.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think that\NByakuya is here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.80,0:12:51.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you that concerned\Nabout him, Ichigo?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.56,0:12:52.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.23,0:12:56.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He joined the Zanpakuto and
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.13,0:12:58.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,pointed his sword\Nat Rukia and Renji.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.69,0:13:02.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't know why.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.20,0:13:09.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My desire… I want…\Nto defend my pride.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.23,0:13:11.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's all.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.30,0:13:15.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I thought you might know\Nwhat Byakuya is thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.27,0:13:16.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know, either!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.60,0:13:17.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.06,0:13:27.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.26,0:13:30.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Simmer down!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.10,0:13:35.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you get worked up, you'll never\Nbe able to bring back Byakuya!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.06,0:13:41.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He probably has\Nsome secret plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.93,0:13:42.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.84,0:13:47.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.63,0:13:54.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.90,0:13:58.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that she was the former\Ncommander of the Stealth Force…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.80,0:14:01.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But she wasn't\Nmuch of a challenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.26,0:14:09.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stealth Hoho, Shiho 3…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.06,0:14:11.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Utsusemi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.20,0:14:23.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up with this?\NGirls these days are all talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.80,0:14:26.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead of me, Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.26,0:14:29.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, saving the Head Captain\Nis our top priority!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.86,0:14:34.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After that, you can do\Nwhatever you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.10,0:14:37.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.50,0:14:58.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.03,0:15:03.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've come to a pretty nice place.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.25,0:15:06.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure are carefree.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.12,0:15:08.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.53,0:15:11.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like we're going to\Nclimb up these steps
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.63,0:15:13.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to go deeper into this tunnel.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.53,0:15:22.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What shall we play?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.83,0:15:25.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wanna play?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.66,0:15:28.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's there?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.52,0:15:30.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He wants to know who we are!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.52,0:15:32.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He does!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.23,0:15:35.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really not\Nknow who we are?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.25,0:15:36.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.26,0:15:41.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,– Come on, let's play!\N– Come on, let's play!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.38,0:15:42.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,– Come on!\N– Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.86,0:15:44.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.35,0:15:48.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we don't play with these kids,\Nwe won't be able to move on.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.93,0:15:49.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.82,0:15:51.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though they're Zanpakuto,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.26,0:15:52.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel uncomfortable\Nplaying with children.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.06,0:15:56.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah… What do we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.83,0:16:02.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then…\NWho are you children?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.38,0:16:03.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who could we be?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.59,0:16:04.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.77,0:16:07.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you Sogyonokotowari?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.72,0:16:09.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,– Correct!\N– Correct!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.63,0:16:12.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He figured it out right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.39,0:16:14.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How boring!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.63,0:16:16.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.53,0:16:18.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did I kill your fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.60,0:16:20.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then let's begin the next game!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.77,0:16:22.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, let's do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.38,0:16:23.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we play?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.91,0:16:25.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about Tosenkyo?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.52,0:16:27.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That sounds great!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.22,0:16:28.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Great!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.70,0:16:30.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.83,0:16:31.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.16,0:16:33.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,– Three!\N– Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.53,0:16:41.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,– All right…\N– All right…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.73,0:16:42.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,– Go!\N– Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.87,0:16:57.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, what shall we play?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.21,0:17:04.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately for you,\Nplaytime is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.73,0:17:06.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.43,0:17:09.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've known each other\Nfor a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.66,0:17:13.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't we just reconcile\Nour differences?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.55,0:17:14.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I refuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.63,0:17:18.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What with your arrogant attitude
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.08,0:17:21.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nwe've run out of patience with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.02,0:17:23.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"We"?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.03,0:17:30.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then that other Spiritual Pressure\NI've been sensing…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.73,0:17:33.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I wasn't imagining it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.91,0:17:55.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You finally came out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.86,0:18:01.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You saved me the time\Nlooking for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.00,0:18:05.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad you could come,\NSoul Reaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.76,0:18:08.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get my revenge for\Nour last encounter!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.97,0:18:15.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is the Old Man's Spiritual Pressure\Ncoming from this way?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.31,0:18:21.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They showed up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.19,0:18:30.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.49,0:19:11.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This Spiritual Pressure…\NIs it the Old Man's?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.89,0:19:12.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.10,0:19:33.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha—?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.17,0:19:43.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Die, Soul Reaper!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.48,0:19:44.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.13,0:19:50.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not letting you go.\NI'm going to reap your life!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.83,0:19:56.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bankai!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.80,0:20:07.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.93,0:20:17.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Getsugatensho!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.58,0:20:39.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.26,0:20:53.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Hisagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.40,0:21:30.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.56,0:21:36.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A barrier, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.56,0:21:42.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez… This is such a pain…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.70,0:21:44.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.11,0:23:24.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My swords are so beautiful.\NI would've never imagined.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.73,0:23:27.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I never expected mine\Nto be children.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.57,0:23:29.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if there's some way I could
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.29,0:23:31.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,just keep them by my side \Nand not fight them.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.52,0:23:33.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I want to play\Nwith them for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.29,0:23:35.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please fight them.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.13,0:23:36.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Illustrated Guide to Soul Reapers!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.59,0:23:38.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say! Say, say, say!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.91,0:23:42.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought I would\Nrun into Yoruichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.53,0:23:44.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's so great about her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.85,0:23:48.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But letting her see me\Nget into danger…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.13,0:23:49.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How shameful!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.63,0:23:51.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's your fault for being weak!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.65,0:23:53.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.53,0:23:59.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoruichi…c-c-c-carried\Nm-me in her arms!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.40,0:24:00.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.89,0:24:01.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you listening?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.77,0:24:04.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoruichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.75,0:24:06.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,